OL,3,C111-year-old crowned world's oldest man
OL,5,FHis care home, The Hollies Rest Home
OL,6,Fin Southport, confirmed the news in a
OL,7,Fsocial media post, with Guinness
OL,8,Fdelivering a framed certificate to
OL,9,FJohn.
OL,11,FThe Hollies said: "Today we had a
OL,12,Fsurprise visit from the World Guinness
OL,13,FRecords, as we have the world's oldest
OL,14,Fliving man here at The Hollies. The
OL,15,Flegend we call John!
OL,17,F"What an absolute honour it is to have
OL,18,Fsuch a well mannered, lovely gentleman
OL,19,Fwith us, we are all so proud.
OL,20,FCongratulations John."
