OL,3,C111-year-old crowned world's oldest man
OL,5,FJohn has is his chippy tea every
OL,6,FFriday.
OL,8,FHe said: "Fish and chips have got to
OL,9,Fbe my favourite dish, it's always been
OL,10,Fsuch a treat, and I think looking
OL,11,Fforward to my next visit to the chippy
OL,12,Fhas kept me young. I feel the same now
OL,13,Fas I did when I was in my 80s, nothing
OL,14,Fhas changed really."
OL,16,FHe was born on 16 August 1912, the
OL,17,Fsame year as the Titanic's maiden
OL,18,Fvoyage, and he has lived through two
OL,19,Fworld wars.
