OL,3,C111-year-old crowned world's oldest man
OL,5,FProblems with his eyesight meant John
OL,6,Fwas given an administrative role with
OL,7,Fthe Royal Mail during the Second World
OL,8,FWar.
OL,10,FHe also used to work as a depot clerk
OL,11,Fand accountant for Shell-Mex and BP,
OL,12,Fand is now a great-grandfather.
OL,14,FHe married his wife, Blodwen, in 1942,
OL,15,Fand welcomed their only child, Susan,
OL,16,Fin 1943, before spending 44 happy
OL,17,Fyears together until Blodwen died in
OL,18,F1986.
