OL,3,C111-year-old crowned world's oldest man
OL,5,FITV News reporter Andrew Fletcher went
OL,6,Fto visit John as he celebrated his
OL,7,F111th birthday in August 2023
OL,9,FJohn, who supports , said keeping
OL,10,Factive and constantly learning has
OL,11,Falso helped to keep his mind sharp.
OL,13,FHe said: "Keeping active is very
OL,14,Fimportant, I've always loved football
OL,15,Fbut when I was younger I was part of
OL,16,Fthe Liverpool Ramblers Association
OL,17,Fwhich went hiking all over the country.
