OL,5,F"We used to meet up at least once a
OL,6,Fmonth, and when all the associations
OL,7,Ffrom all over the UK met up once a
OL,8,Fyear we could fill an entire train.
OL,10,F"The Rambler's Associations don't
OL,11,Freally exist anymore and I haven't
OL,12,Fbeen hiking for quite some years but I
OL,13,Flargely carry on here as I would if I
OL,14,Fwas still living independently."
